title: Two Turkeys on Thanksgiving Wrecking their Corvettes in The Woodlands
description: Check out the REMIX: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q5SjKE... I shot this video of 2 Corvettes drag racing on my way to pick up our Thanksgiving Turkey. I had a feeling something bad was going to happen b/c of the conditions and testosterone flowing between these two. No one was hurt, only the drivers egos.
